-- General Motors India Workers Strike at Gujarat Plant, Bloomberg UTV Says
-- B y   S i d d h a r t h   P h i l i p
-- 2010-10-29T04:49:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-29/general-motors-india-workers-strike-at-gujarat-plant-bloomberg-utv-says.html
About 700 employees at General
Motors Co.’s plant in the western Indian state of Gujarat went
on strike demanding higher wages, Bloomberg UTV reported today,
citing people it didn’t identify.  P.Balendran, a spokesman for GM’s India unit, didn’t answer
calls made on his mobile phone.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Siddharth Philip in Mumbai at 
 sphilip3@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
